SECURED AND MONITORED WEB INFRASTRUCTURE

FIREWALLS: Filter traffic, block unauthorized access, protect servers.
HTTPS: Encrypts traffic, prevents data interception.
SSL CERT: Added to serve www.foobar.com over HTTPS.
MONITORING: Tracks health, detects failures, analyzes traffic.
MONITORING CLIENTS: Agents collect metrics and send to Sumo Logic.
QPS MONITORING: Configure agent to count Nginx requests per second.

ISSUES:
1. SSL termination at load balancer: internal traffic unencrypted.
2. Single MySQL Primary: if it fails, no writes possible.
3. Same components on all servers: resource competition, harder to scale.
